data.description: SHORT SALE! CASH ONLY NO CONTINGENCY CONTRACTS ONLY. This wonderful home is only one block to the beach, beach walkway, restaurants and entertainment. Make this your two bedroom two bath home and go to the beach every day. Features include THREE WALK-IN CLOSETS, two large bedrooms, Juliet balcony and more. This is a very low price to be this close to the beach. The building is currently doing concrete restoration and getting a new roof soon. Hot water heater installed 7/2014 and the AC installed 1/2014. Buyers can still get financing.
